## How to Update This Register

**Add a row when:**
- A new MCP server is installed (Status: Open until checklist passes)
- A new AI agent or tool is adopted
- An incident occurs that this register did not anticipate
- A new CVE is published for any tool in the stack
- A risk pattern is observed that isn't listed

**Update status when:**
- A mitigation is put in place (Open → Mitigated)
- A mitigated risk recurs (Mitigated → Open)
- A risk is permanently eliminated (any → Closed)

**Review cadence:** Monthly for active projects. After major releases. After
any security incident in the AI toolchain.
